test.sql: SELECT o.OrderId, o.CustomerId, o.EmployeeId FROM Orders o WHERE o.Freight <= ALL ( SELECT Year(o.OrderDate) * SUM(p.UnitPrice) FROM [Order Details] od INNER JOIN Products p ON p.ProductID = od.ProductID WHERE od.OrderID = o.OrderID ) ORDER BY 1, 2, 3

property.name: Predicate
property.value: Expr1010 IS NULL OR o.Freight IS NULL OR o.Freight > Expr1010
